make your case in one sentence or less.

00:48.500 --> 00:51.060
Ladies and daughters first.

00:52.230 --> 00:53.610
Go.

00:53.740 --> 00:55.800
The burden of proof is
on posner and klein,okay?

00:55.840 --> 01:00.330
We don't want to risk opening you up to cross-examination
to show that they haven't met their burden.

01:00.400 --> 01:03.510
We do if we don't want to take the greater
risk of appearing that we have no other way

01:03.560 --> 01:08.590
of demonstrating that you have all your faculties,which,by
the way,testifying will do very effectively.

01:08.670 --> 01:10.670
