you tell me you haven't
been reading dad's journal.

07:00.390 --> 07:03.640
- I haven't been reading dad's journal.
- Well,skimming it,then.

07:03.770 --> 07:04.400
You have!

07:04.510 --> 07:07.670
Look,he said that you
take the lead case.

07:07.690 --> 07:09.690
I mean,he wrote down the clients' names!

07:09.750 --> 07:12.780
When I saw the kims' names
in here,I nearly had a stroke.

07:12.840 --> 07:14.310
Look,I-I-I
dog-eared the page.

07:14.390 --> 07:15.910
- Nate.-
Yeah,o-okay.

07:16.110 --> 07:20.460
- I-I'm sure that you associate the journal with
grace,and that doesn't- this is not about her.

07:20.570 --> 07:25.390
This is about me not wanting to live my life
according to dad's unabomber prophecy manifesto.

07:25.450 --> 07:27.500
If you only knew these people
and what they've been through--

07:27.550 --> 07:29.000
but I don't,nate.I don't know them.

07:29.080 --> 07:31.310
I know jordan,and I know
what he's going through,

07:31.350 --> 07:34.920
