08:26.690 --> 08:28.790
werewolves,transmigration.

08:28.940 --> 08:31.620
Kind of like the buddhist
version of "the x-files."

08:31.840 --> 08:33.400
And what's his name doing in the book?

08:33.490 --> 08:35.720
I-I studied acupuncture under him.

08:36.669 --> 08:38.960
He taught me a technique.

08:39.220 --> 08:41.659
He called it "the dark truth."

08:41.880 --> 08:43.450
"The dark truth"?

08:43.520 --> 08:48.040
It's old medicine-- supposed to
bring mental clarity through pain.

08:48.100 --> 08:49.590
You're making this up.

08:49.660 --> 08:51.240
Well,only insofar as I'm
just educated-guessing.

08:51.300 --> 08:54.090
But it doesn't make a difference,because
I'm not ing this on you.

08:54.120 --> 08:56.020
It's too dangerous.

08:56.110 --> 08:58.510
Well,I already clearly have
the written consent of a parent.

08:58.840 --> 09:00.270
Come on.This is about jordan.

09:00.300 --> 09:02.220
I need to know,frank.

09:07.590 --> 09:09.970
And now for something
completely different.

09:10.350 --> 09:12.760
Take a deep breath.

09:16.830 --> 09:18.700
do it.

09:34.910 --> 09:36.850
someone call security.

09:37.020 --> 09:40.600
Who let this man in here?

09:43.100 --> 09:44.690
I'm just kidding,man.

09:44.760 --> 09:45.920
Good to see ya.

09:46.010 --> 09:48.450
How long has it been--
uh,like six months?

09:48.790 --> 09:50.830
Saw you this morning.

09:51.050 --> 09:53.760
Uh... yeah.

09:53.880 --> 09:56.760
Did the "wethersby" fall off?

10:00.490 --> 10:03.950
Is this little trip down memory
lane part of you coming to grips

10:04.000 --> 10:07.200
with getting your ass spanked on
jordan's hearing six months ago?

10:07.250 --> 10:08.470
Six months?

10:08.540 --> 10:13.030
Okay.I don't suppose you paid extra
for the warranty on your brain surgery.

10:13.050 --> 10:15.980
It sounds like you might
need a little tune-up.

10:16.040 --> 10:17.860
What happened in the hearing?

10:17.940 --> 10:25.170
Oh,about what you'd expect to happen when a lawyer
is crazier thanhe alleged crazy guy he's defending,

10:25.350 --> 10:27.170
as this little reunion shows.

10:27.270 --> 10:30.490
- It was my fault.
- Hey,don't be so hard on yourself.

10:31.420 --> 10:33.710
that's my job.

10:39.000 --> 10:41.100
eli,take it easy.You're back.

10:41.160 --> 10:43.460
What did you see?Eli?

10:43.610 --> 10:45.010
can you repeat that?

10:45.110 --> 10:46.380
I have to withdraw from your case.

10:46.450 --> 10:48.270
- Excuse me?- I know this
comes as a surprise,but--

10:48.340 --> 10:51.570
I seem to recall a rather
impassioned argument about

10:51.630 --> 10:55.510
how this hearing was the most important
moment in my professional life,

10:55.610 --> 10:59.770
and there was no one better suited
to steer me through it than you.

10:59.820 --> 11:02.710
I know,sir,but I think I was wrong.

11:02.770 --> 11:05.860
You should go with taylor,and
just taylor,on this one.

11:06.020 --> 11:09.540
I would just drag you down,believe me.

11:10.930 --> 11:13.040
You're absolutely right,eli.

11:14.110 --> 11:18.990
If you were planning on exhibiting this
kind of capricious judgment on my behalf,

11:19.530 --> 11:23.000
I wouldn't be well-served
by you representing me.

11:23.540 --> 11:27.690
- Taylor...
- do what you need to do.

11:34.750 --> 11:36.620
We're fine.

11:37.040 --> 11:38.790
I'm fine.

11:38.860 --> 11:40.750
I can do this.Don't worry.

11:49.850 --> 11:51.140
S-something I did?

11:51.230 --> 11:52.680
More like something you didn't do.

11:52.730 --> 11:55.930
I can't believe you,of all
people,bailing on jordan.

11:56.000 --> 11:57.400
It's like you chose a side.

11:57.440 --> 12:01.210
I didn't choose anything.I got
one of my 9-1-1 calls from god.

12:01.310 --> 12:05.850
Then you star-69 him and say you'll take
care of it after you take care of jordan.

12:05.910 --> 12:07.360
It doesn't work that way.

12:07.420 --> 12:09.440
Trust me,you want me
off the jordan case.

12:09.480 --> 12:11.260
You really do.

12:13.460 --> 12:14.520
What's this?

12:14.620 --> 12:18.470
Lead paint product liability.It's david
versus goliath stuff--your favorite.

12:18.570 --> 12:20.350
- Just read it.
- Well,I don't have to read it.

12:20.480 --> 12:23.970
There's nothing in this file that could
make me want to abandon our mentor.

12:24.860 --> 12:27.270
firstly,he's not your mentor.

12:27.410 --> 12:29.400
Secondly,I didn't abandon him.

12:29.450 --> 12:32.920
Taylor's handling it,and believe
me,she's happier that I no longer am.

12:32.970 --> 12:36.480
And thirdly,I'm doing this
with or without your help.

12:36.550 --> 12:39.120
And we both know that you're biologically
incapable of turning down a poor,

12:39.200 --> 12:41.570
sick kid case like this one.

12:41.940 --> 12:43.410
I hate you.

12:43.620 --> 12:45.840
That's a lot of discovery for a
simple breach of contract case.

12:45.920 --> 12:47.000
I know.

12:47.100 --> 12:48.600
I'm an artist.

12:49.490 --> 12:51.270
Uh,can you give us a minute,buddy?

12:51.340 --> 12:52.700
Absolutely.

12:52.780 --> 12:53.800
I'm here for keith,actually.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.130
- Him?
- Me?

12:55.230 --> 12:58.740
I need to replace eli on
posner and klein vs.Wethersby.

12:59.010 --> 13:02.210
Well,I'm kind of busy helping matt
draft discovery requests in koehler.

13:02.420 --> 13:06.560
I'm sure matt won't mind,especially considering
how important my father's case is to him.

13:06.920 --> 13:08.880
100%.

13:08.960 --> 13:12.560
Jordan needs a capable and
objective lawyer on his team.

13:20.290 --> 13:22.990
Leesie started having
seizures when she was 3.

13:23.100 --> 13:25.510
We hug her till she stops shaking.

13:25.530 --> 13:27.590
It's the only thing we can do.

13:27.640 --> 13:34.640
And when she started school this year,her teacher
told us she was slower than the other kids.

13:35.260 --> 13:39.050
We're not spiteful people,mr.Stone,and
we've never sued anyone.

13:39.600 --> 13:44.150
But leesie's doctor's bills-- they're more than
I make in a year,and I'm already working two jobs.

13:44.200 --> 13:48.370
Did you ever actually see
leesie ingest paint chips?

13:48.680 --> 13:55.590
No,but when she was a toddler,everything she
could get her little hands on went into her mouth.

13:55.750 --> 13:57.540
