14:18.210 --> 14:19.690
I-I don't understand.

14:19.740 --> 14:22.920
Well,if your apartment was
constructed in the 1950s,

14:23.310 --> 14:26.600
that means it's got at least two
decades worth of lead paint in it.

14:26.670 --> 14:29.970
It's highly unlikely that that
paint is from a single manufacturer.

14:30.010 --> 14:34.650
So even if we stood a chance of
bringing a successful lawsuit,

14:34.760 --> 14:37.240
we wouldn't know which one to sue.

14:37.760 --> 14:39.550
so what do we do?

14:39.610 --> 14:41.660
We sue them all.

14:56.950 --> 15:00.600
if you don't mind,I'd like it to be just
me and leesie at the plaintiff's table.

15:00.670 --> 15:02.390
You're demoting me to the gallery?

15:02.490 --> 15:04.290
- Very mature,eli.
- It's not like that.

15:04.410 --> 15:05.860
It's just,gibbons is gonna
have an army in there.

15:05.910 --> 15:08.500
I want it to be as few people
as possible at our table.

15:08.550 --> 15:11.880
Sympathy is our best and only play here.

15:12.140 --> 15:13.980
Okay.

15:24.550 --> 15:27.490
frankly,I'd always been
in awe of jordan wethersby.

15:27.540 --> 15:29.610
The man was single-minded.

15:29.670 --> 15:33.460
It was rare finding a man
whose tenacity exceeded my own.

15:33.630 --> 15:36.870
You can imagine my surprise when I get
a phone call out of the literal blue,

15:36.950 --> 15:41.650
telling me he could "no longer in
good conscience" represent my company.

15:41.700 --> 15:43.300
Did he explain why?

15:43.350 --> 15:48.360
He registered some moral indignation regarding
the wages we pay at our sri lanka factory.

15:48.400 --> 15:50.910
It was like I didn't
even know the man anymore.

15:50.950 --> 15:52.580
- Objection.
- Sustained.

15:52.620 --> 15:54.040
