34:19.810 --> 34:23.530
My clients got the proverbial
offer they couldn't refuse.

34:24.830 --> 34:26.770
You won,right?

34:26.889 --> 34:29.460
I heard the judge ruled that
none of your screws are loose.

34:29.550 --> 34:30.770
Yes.

34:30.909 --> 34:34.520
Unfortunately,in taking my case to
trial,I lost the support of the board,

34:34.780 --> 34:38.380
which I suspect was martin
and marci's gambit all along.

34:38.460 --> 34:45.420
- So they...
- they voted me out as managing partner 20 minutes ago.

34:46.320 --> 34:48.580
Uh... I'm sorry,sir.

34:48.719 --> 34:53.570
It could've been worse.I could have lost
the case entirely,been branded a psychotic.

34:53.850 --> 34:56.560
Had my license to practice
called into question.

34:56.980 --> 35:00.600
Given how they went at me
through you,I have no doubt all

35:00.620 --> 35:07.530
that would've transpired had you been my
attorney during this instead of merely my friend.

35:09.160 --> 35:10.800
Your friend?

35:10.900 --> 35:16.470
What better term for someone I care
deeply about and admire even more?

35:16.640 --> 35:19.140
I just thought that after
the other night and..

35:19.180 --> 35:26.840
friends fight,eli,and the other night,I
couldn't indulge in supreme court prophecies.

35:27.780 --> 35:31.470
today,however,I could use
something to look forward to.

35:32.110 --> 35:33.870
Sorry,sir.

35:34.420 --> 35:37.440
It doesn't look like we'll be going
to the supreme court after all.

35:38.300 --> 35:40.430
We all have visions,eli.

35:40.490 --> 35:44.570
I had a vision for what
this firm would become.

35:45.140 --> 35:48.200
Sometimes we have to readjust our plans.

35:48.440 --> 35:52.810
If we're not meant to go to the supreme
court with this case,perhaps another.

35:53.580 --> 35:56.240
This case needs to go
to the supreme court.

35:57.580 --> 36:00.050
But maybe what it doesn't need is us.

36:03.540 --> 36:05.550
what are you gonna do now?

36:06.380 --> 36:12.740
I'd considered golf as an option,but the accident
the other week has left my lower back in spasm.

36:12.820 --> 36:17.320
That leaves me no other option
than to continue practicing law.

36:21.380 --> 36:26.930
I intend to create the kind of practice
I've been expelled for proposing.

36:29.650 --> 36:33.140
Might I entice you to follow
your old boss to a new firm?

36:34.560 --> 36:36.670
No.

36:37.640 --> 36:40.520
But I'll follow my friend.

36:45.580 --> 36:46.870
What's the catch?

36:46.910 --> 36:48.210
no catch.

36:48.260 --> 36:50.380
So you just want to hand over
a brilliantly thought out,

36:50.470 --> 36:52.810
fully developed case file
against the paint industry?

36:52.840 --> 36:55.330
Well,not the whole case.You still
have to find yourself a client.

36:55.380 --> 36:59.880
My point is,this is
big,like big tobacco big.

36:59.930 --> 37:01.320
Why me?

37:01.370 --> 37:03.000
We're not exactly besties.

37:03.030 --> 37:05.690
Which is why no one will suspect
you got the information from me.

37:07.670 --> 37:11.310
This public nuisance theory of yours,it could
make it all the way to the state supreme court.

37:11.380 --> 37:13.000
Federal,even.

37:13.070 --> 37:14.470
Are you about to be indicted?

37:14.550 --> 37:16.790
Sorry,you're not that lucky,jeff.

37:17.120 --> 37:18.360
No,I just...

37:18.440 --> 37:21.520
I realized that this has to
be someone else's crusade.

37:30.190 --> 37:32.220
I'm sorry it had to come to this.

37:32.280 --> 37:34.510
Somehow you'll manage,I imagine.

37:35.500 --> 37:38.720
You can stay on as of counsel.

37:39.190 --> 37:42.680
In fact,marci and i have discussed
it.We would very much like you to.

37:42.760 --> 37:45.710
Well,that's a very magnanimous
consolation prize,martin.

37:45.850 --> 37:49.820
I have some rather specific anatomical
suggestions as to what you can do with it.

37:50.000 --> 37:52.630
I trust that when administration
sends me my things,

37:52.680 --> 37:56.720
you'll remember that many of the paintings
here are from my personal collection.

37:56.780 --> 37:58.890
Sorry.Am I interrupting?

37:58.970 --> 38:00.490
we were just leaving.

38:00.610 --> 38:02.930
Stay.You'll want to hear this.

38:04.320 --> 38:07.430
Your testimony about the cocktail
napkin reminded me of something.

38:07.640 --> 38:12.820
One of my very first assignments when I joined
W.P.K. Was to review the firm's real estate holdings.

38:12.880 --> 38:14.550
- So?
- Uh,15 years ago,

38:14.630 --> 38:17.440
when you expanded the firm
to this location,martin,

38:17.500 --> 38:22.880
you were involved in that bitter divorce,and,marci,you
were under investigation for insider trading.

38:22.940 --> 38:26.220
I was exonerated of those false charges.

38:26.350 --> 38:27.950
Yes,happy times.

38:28.060 --> 38:31.230
Because of the clouds hanging
over your respective heads,

38:31.520 --> 38:36.080
the three of you decided to put this
building solely in my father's name.

38:36.940 --> 38:38.370
Now the three of you may
have signed that napkin,

38:38.430 --> 38:42.690
but only my father's name is
on the title to this building.

38:50.840 --> 38:57.220
Well... marci,martin,it appears
you're trespassing on my property.

38:57.650 --> 39:01.780
But I can be gracious,give the attorneys
here time to decide if they want to stay.

39:02.940 --> 39:05.800
A week sounds fair,doesn't it?

39:20.760 --> 39:22.720
Don't worry.I didn't read it.

39:22.850 --> 39:27.660
Although I was tempted to make sure george
lucas didn't make any more "star wars" movies.

39:29.010 --> 39:30.850
What stopped you?

39:31.070 --> 39:37.820
I don't want to live my life according to what
I think some notations in some book might say.

39:39.430 --> 39:43.830
I don't want to try to control
the uncontrollable anymore.

39:54.470 --> 39:56.800
That was... bold.

39:57.250 --> 40:01.850
"Bold" would have been reading
it or asking you what it said.

40:02.300 --> 40:05.870
You're gonna take long strides
on the surface of the earth,eli.

40:06.910 --> 40:11.570
And with every step,you're
gonna change the world.

40:11.730 --> 40:13.740
That was in the book?

40:13.940 --> 40:15.790
Doesn't matter.

40:15.930 --> 40:18.210
That's what I believe.

40:46.840 --> 40:48.890
jeff.

40:50.580 --> 40:52.740
Eli.

40:52.930 --> 40:56.080
Maggie,what are you doing here?

40:56.200 --> 40:57.410
What are you doing here?

40:57.490 --> 41:00.290
oyez,oyez,oyez!

41:00.930 --> 41:02.840
All persons having business
before the honorable,

41:02.900 --> 41:06.920
the supreme court of the united states,are
admonished to draw near and give their attention,

41:07.030 --> 41:08.640
for the court is now sitting.

41:19.170 --> 41:21.980
Mr. Chief justice,and
may it please the court,

41:22.050 --> 41:24.700
my name is maggie dekker of
posner,klein,and associates

